---
title: Szechuan Pork & Green Bean Stir-Fry with Peanuts & Jasmine Rice
description: Forget takeout: the path to sweet-spicy-savory dinner bliss is as simple as breaking out a frying pan! In this recipe, ground pork and green beans are coated in tantalizing szechuan sauce and peanuts are transformed into the perfect crunchy topping thanks to a sugary coating. Everything comes together over a bed of steamy rice mixed with warm, sizzly ginger—in 30 minutes, no less! The results? A symphony of flavors and textures that are so delicious, you might just lick the plate.
